modName: Muffle Heimskr - The Preacher in Whiterun
summary: If your bugged by the constant screaming from Heimskr now you can silence him without killing him.
descriptionHtml:
Another file in the Muffle Series, I bring you Muffle Heimskr - The Preacher in Whiterun. If your bugged by the constant screaming from Heimskr now you can silence him without killing him. This comes in 2 flavors, Muffle Heimskr - Quiet and Muffle Heimskr - Mute. Choose only one.
